   set {_MenuCollection-RottenFlesh-9.%UUID of arg-1%} to red stained glass pane
  else:
   set {_MenuCollection-RottenFlesh-9.%UUID of arg-1%} to lime stained glass pane

  open virtual chest inventory with size 6 named "Collection de Chair Putréfiée" to arg-1
  wait 1 tick
  format gui slot (integers between 0 and 53) of arg-1 with black stained glass pane named "&f"

  format gui slot 4 of arg-1 with rotten flesh named "&eChair Putréfiée %{Collection-RottenFlesh.%UUID of arg-1%}%" with lore "&7Consultez tous les progrès et récompenses" and "&7de votre collection de Chair Putréfiée!" and "&7" and "&7Vous avez récolté &e%{Collection-RottenFlesh-Collected.%UUID of arg-1%}%&7."

  format gui slot 18 of arg-1 with {_MenuCollection-RottenFlesh-1.%UUID of arg-1%} named "&eChair Putréfiée I" with lore "&7Consultez la progression et la récompense!" and "&7" and "&7Récompense" and "&8???" and "&7" and "&7Nécessite &b50 Chairs Putréfiées"

  format gui slot 19 of arg-1 with {_MenuCollection-RottenFlesh-2.%UUID of arg-1%} named "&eChair Putréfiée II" with lore "&7Consultez la progression et la récompense!" and "&7" and "&7Récompense" and "&8???" and "&7" and "&7Nécessite &b100 Chairs Putréfiées"

